    "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" lang=\"en\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" />\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"nofollow\" />\n<title>TA558 - Threat Group Cards: A Threat Actor Encyclopedia</title>\n<link href=\"/style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n</head>\n<body class=\"mbody\">\n<div class=\"logos\">\n<table border=\"0\"><tr><td><a href=\"https://www.etda.or.th\"><img src=\"/img/logo-etda.png\" height=\"50\" alt=\"ETDA\" title=\"Visit the ETDA website\" /></a></td>\n<td><font size=\"3\">สำนักงานพัฒนาธุรกรรมทางอิเล็กทรอนิกส์<br />Electronic Transactions Development Agency</font></td></tr></table>\n</div>\n<link href=\"/menubar.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n<div id=\"menubar\">\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi\">Groups</a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listtools.cgi\">Tools</a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptsearch.cgi\">Search</a>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptstats.cgi\">Statistics</a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"graph\">\n<div class=\"gline\"><img src=\"/img/clear.gif\" width=\"1\" height=\"3\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<div><img src=\"/img/report.jpg\" width=\"900\" alt=\"Report\" /></div>\n<a name=\"top\"></a>\n<div class=\"searchdiv\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptsearch.cgi\" title=\"Search the database\" class=\"inlink\">Search</a></div>\n<div class=\"outermain\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/aptgroups.cgi\" class=\"inlink\" title=\"Home\">Home</a> &gt; <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi\" class=\"inlink\" title=\"List all groups\">List all groups</a> &gt; TA558</div>\n<h1>Threat Group Cards: A Threat Actor Encyclopedia</h1>\n<div class=\"innermainov\">\n<h3><a href=\"/cgi-bin/showcard.cgi?u=2a612bf1-4cfd-436e-90d5-e104966d1f50\" title=\"Get permanent link to this card\" class=\"inlink\"><img src=\"/img/link.png\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Permanent link\" /></a> APT group: TA558</h3>\n<table width=\"100%\" class=\"tborder\">\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Names</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">TA558 <i><font size=\"-2\">",
    "</font></i></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Country</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">[Unknown]</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Motivation</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?m=Financial%20crime\" title=\"Search for all threat groups with motivation Financial crime\" class=\"inlink\">Financial crime</a></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">First seen</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">2018</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Description</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">",
    "Since 2018, Proofpoint has tracked a financially-motivated cybercrime actor, TA558, targeting hospitality, travel, and related industries located in Latin America and sometimes North America, and western Europe. The actor sends malicious emails written in Portuguese, Spanish, and sometimes English. The emails use reservation-themed lures with business-relevant themes such as hotel room bookings. The emails may contain malicious attachments or URLs aiming to distribute one of at least 15 different malware payloads, typically remote access trojans",
    ", that can enable reconnaissance, data theft, and distribution of follow-on payloads.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Observed</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">Sectors: <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Construction\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Construction\" class=\"inlink\">Construction</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Education\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Education\" class=\"inlink\">Education</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Energy\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Energy\" class=\"inlink\">Energy</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Financial\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Financial\" class=\"inlink\">Financial</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Government\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Government\" class=\"inlink\">Government</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Hospitality\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Hospitality\" class=\"inlink\">Hospitality</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Industrial\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Industrial\" class=\"inlink\">Industrial</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=IT\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target IT\" class=\"inlink\">IT</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Pharmaceutical\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Pharmaceutical\" class=\"inlink\">Pharmaceutical</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Transportation\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Transportation\" class=\"inlink\">Transportation</a>.<br />Countries: <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=Algeria\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Algeria\" class=\"inlink\">Algeria</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=Argentina\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Argentina\" class=\"inlink\">Argentina</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?v=Brazil\"