/us/blog/threat-insight/reservations-requested-ta558-targets-hospitality-and-travel\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.proofpoint.com/us/blog/threat-insight/reservations-requested-ta558-targets-hospitality-and-travel</a>&gt;</td></tr>\n</table>\n<p>Last change to this card: 22 April 2024</p>\n<p>Download this actor card in <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=TA558&o=p\" title=\"Download this card in PDF format\" class=\"inlink\">PDF</a> or <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=TA558&o=j\" title=\"Download this card in JSON format\" class=\"inlink\">JSON</a> format</p>\n<div class=\"backtotop\"><a href=\"#top\" title=\"Back to the top\" class=\"inlink\">&uarr;</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr><td width=\"80%\" rowspan=\"4\" valign=\"top\">\n<p>Infrastructure and Security Department<br />\nElectronic Transactions Development Agency</p>\n<h3>Follow us on</h3>\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/ETDA.Thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-facebook.png\" alt=\"Facebook\" title=\"Follow us on Facebook\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/etda_thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-twitter.png\" alt=\"Twitter\" title=\"Follow us on Twitter\" /></a>\n</td><td colspan=\"2\">\n<h3>Report incidents</h3>\n</td>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"0%\"><img src=\"/img/icon-phone.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" alt=\"Telephone\" title=\"Telephone\" /></td>\n<td width=\"20%\"><strong>+66"
